 GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/69a03121c4364c4b81782d6b1d32e820\" img_width=\"750\" img_height=\"564\" alt=\"全亚洲仅此一台的“神”车，到底是个什么来头？\" inline=\"0\" data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p></div><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（奥地利Turracher高地冬季试车时候的quattro原型车）</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">先从阿波罗缔造者创始人Roland Gumpert 先生说起，Roland 先生早年是奥迪汽车的底盘和动力总成领域的部门领导。当时他参与了德国国防军越野车项目的研发设计，那台车就是全轮驱动的大众Iltis，但实际上车上的零部件大多来自奥迪，除了名字外，它是一台彻头彻尾的奥迪Iltis。随后Roland先生给皮耶希提出了建议：<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">把全轮驱动这一系统放进民用轿车里去。</span>于是乎，Iltis的整套动力总成就移植到了奥迪轿车上，传说中的quattro就此诞生了！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/19596a00935947b4acbe6d9b27b2f87a\" img_width=\"750\" img_height=\"499\" alt=\"全亚洲仅此一台的“神”车，到底是个什么来头？\" inline=\"0\" data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p></div><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/65ec2177c44a44b5946b01ee4024b624\" img_width=\"750\" img_height=\"496\" alt=\"全亚洲仅此一台的“神”车，到底是个什么来头？\" inline=\"0\" data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p></div><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">70年代末，当时几乎没有多少人相信全轮驱动在轿车上是可行的，<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">但是Roland先生强烈建议奥迪把带有quattro的赛车拿到WRC世界拉力锦标赛赛场</span>。因为当时的原型车仅仅靠4着条夏季轮胎就爬上了高难度的积雪路面，董事会的小伙伴们一看都惊呆了……然后奥迪就开始“浪”了。1980年的巴黎-达喀尔拉力赛，Iltis拿到了第1/2/4名，quattro在WRC的成功向世人证明了4轮驱动完胜了2轮驱动。 随后在1982到1986年他担任了奥迪汽车运动部门的负责人，<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">在他的领导下，奥迪获得了4次世界拉力冠军赛的冠军</span>。</p><h1 class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px; margin: 36px 0px 22px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\">·为什么要打造一台Gumpert Apollo？</span></h1><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/446a9b9e67bd4e4fb3690cb647020dc3\" img_width=\"750\" img_height=\"501\" alt=\"全亚洲仅此一台的“神”车，到底是个什么来头？\" inline=\"0\" data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p></div><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（2008年Gumpert Apollo Sport以1:17.1的圈速登顶Top Gear，2009年又以7:11.57刷新纽博格林北环量产车最快圈速纪录 ）</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">关于为什么会自己去打造一台车？Gumpert先生认为，当自己身为工程师设计制造汽车的时候，<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">每一次的新车发售似乎是一个“谎言”</span>，因为新款车型通常是在老款基础上改造而来的，但是出于设备成本等等各种原因有很多部件沿用老车型。然后用小改款的手段去告诉大家那是一台新车，而掩盖骨子里那是一台旧车的事实。Gumpert先生认为这是对顾客的一种欺骗，加上预算的限制，却又改变不了什么。所以，这是他选择自己去研发一部汽车的初衷。</p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/c7ac36992bb7408ebcf95999c8c0be32\" img_width=\"1080\" img_height=\"608\" alt=\"全亚洲仅此一台的“神”车，到底是个什么来头？\" inline=\"0\" data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p></div><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Gumpert Apollo是一台可以合法上路的赛车，在Gumpert先生试乘其他汽车品牌的跑车时，在无限速高速公路上驾驶没有任何问题。但是上了赛道之后，一些跑车就会出现刹车失效、引擎过热、变速箱损坏等问题<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">。他希望Gumpert的顾客可以把车子直接开上赛道浪完之后，还能顺利地开着它回家，这就是造车的首要目标。</span>Apollo源自于纯粹，它就是一张白纸，不存在从老款车型上拔下来零件去堆砌一台新车。从头到脚一干二净，同时这也是为什么Apollo能够刷新纽博格林北环的圈速记录的原因之一。</p><h1 class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px; margin: 36px 0px 22px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\">·亚洲仅此1台！</span></h1><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &q